{"tid":833544,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【中秋已港化】大坑300人舞火龍祈福   引過百市民觀賞","createTime":"2018-09-23T15:00:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-23T15:26:50.000Z","uid":79563,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c954b933fbd518e21c31797d0ba24a45b84f31ca","tid":833544,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T15:00:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>如果世上有所謂「漢化」，咁大坑無火龍就係「港化」</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180923/large/1537711719_6091.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180923%2Flarge%2F1537711719_6091.jpg&h=0bc20ed4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180923/58716497\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180923%2F58716497&d=YiQ0ngMPxCLw3zTHWrzy757TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=43b0099a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180923%2F58716497&h=07fd53e7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180923/58716497</a><br />\n<br />\n有逾130年歷史的大坑舞火龍，昨迎月夜起一連三晚於大坑揭開序幕，吸引大批巿民及遊客觀賞。全長67公尺的火龍，在300人舞動下浩浩盪盪出發，為巿民祈求平安幸福，遠離災害。<br />\n<br />\n大坑舞火龍一如往年，入夜起開始吸引攝影發燒友、數百名巿民及遊客站於浣紗街兩旁鐵欄外觀賞及拍照，主辦單位大坑坊眾福利會昨傍晚先在蓮花宮舉行開光儀式，由約300名村民及前村民組成的隊伍陸續點香，然後插於龍頭及龍身，由兩名壯男舞動兩個形似球狀的龍珠，引領着48公斤龍頭趨前邁進。<br />\n<br />\n火龍晚上8時許開始巡遊，並在街頭騰龍舞動，線香洩出的火光濺於頭排觀眾身上，但各人均不介意，驚嘆及歡呼聲此起彼落，火龍沿浣紗街、京街等地穿梭，至晚上10時許才落幕，人潮始漸消散。<br />\n<br />\n大坑舞火龍始於1880年，相傳大坑村在一次風災後出現一條大蟒蛇，被村民擊斃，豈料翌日蛇屍不翼而飛，大坑村隨即爆發瘟疫，奪去多人性命，其後有長輩在夢中獲菩薩報夢指點，只要用草紮成草龍，再插滿香枝，於中秋佳節晚上舞動及燃點炮竹，便可驅除瘟疫，自此成為該村傳統活動。"},{"pid":"931d67f8ff908b47b604daf7a83ce71e2e7345ea","tid":833544,"uid":28800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T15:03:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6cbb92d6d6a8e14726cbadd3920df40928f14a3b","tid":833544,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T15:12:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kiss.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4be00e6f8ec7e8e7151bd00d7a8c0c9c9707f587","tid":833544,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T15:14:01.000Z","msg":"冰皮月餅都係將中秋港化<br />\n<br />\n如果世上有「漢化」概念<br />\n<br />\n咁大家都應該明白對應既「粵化」及「港化」"},{"pid":"a9b09c2cc39248275ef4336a4750bc0c44ce7574","tid":833544,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T15:15:20.000Z","msg":"好似仲有度都有舞火龍 但冇咁出名"},{"pid":"52ce95d0950613e40705cac2f1a3075d11c85db3","tid":833544,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9b09c2cc39248275ef4336a4750bc0c44ce7574","tid":833544,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T15:15:20.000Z","msg":"好似仲有度都有舞火龍 但冇咁出名"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T15:18:42.000Z","msg":"所謂出名只係政府商業化既宣傳啫，<br />\n另一度舞火龍好似係薄扶林村。"},{"pid":"04f3797e6c2e51528fb18127567eeda223b16416","tid":833544,"uid":69213,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T15:21:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a776c95412827793ad678c4694c6d29c66f63c27","tid":833544,"uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"04f3797e6c2e51528fb18127567eeda223b16416","tid":833544,"uid":69213,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T15:21:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T15:26:50.000Z","msg":"你條支那狗都好厚臉皮"}]}